{"tid":1022790,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"王心凌\bJ圖專輯封面","createTime":"2019-02-15T09:16:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T09:59:33.000Z","uid":160973,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4624b365a23a2ada5ff39c8ed255f4152f3bd590","tid":1022790,"uid":160973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T09:16:03.000Z","msg":"台灣女歌手王心凌這張新專輯找出新路向，獲讚進步和有蛻變，她以女孩子的甜美方式，探討糖衣底下的黑色矛盾，頗為獨到，音樂班底集合陳珊妮、Jerry C、葛大為、倪子岡、小寒等華語音樂人，有質素保證，音樂風格嘗試電音、R&amp;B、Reggae、Folk到搖滾，甚至唱一小段台語歌，都予人新鮮感。主打歌《在青春迷失的咖啡館》是陳珊妮為王心凌打造，展露率性氣質。抒情歌《大眠》由製作人張簡君創作，施人誠填詞，用獨特觀點解構愛情，觸及情感綁架、道德勒索，切入點頗深。來自美國的CJ Baran創作《劈你的雷正在路上》，令人聽得想跳舞。《到處不存在的我》有少許台語歌詞，結他與弦樂四重奏下，感覺不陳舊，反而很新鮮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2SVfGbi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2SVfGbi&d=rje4l1xmTn6y9o%2BHBfPafyEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=3aa11dd2\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2SVfGbi</a>"},{"pid":"306d4b31e9e0f2372d8c406201d67a8d30f57aad","tid":1022790,"uid":135957,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T05:01:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1df72738cfbf0ce18550c3552bb9494921098d60","tid":1022790,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T05:03:42.000Z","msg":"仲諗住入嚟睇大岩蛇"},{"pid":"a8159da7d1a9d5eaf90b498dc0f73a6d1ff520a1","tid":1022790,"uid":19676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T05:03:52.000Z","msg":"佢個樣好似整容失敗咁"},{"pid":"9595089d1a3b81f510aee6eac1b4bfc9bc2f0ee4","tid":1022790,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T05:04:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201707/67d13899ef5d2f2c56da22db29d575ed.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201707%2F67d13899ef5d2f2c56da22db29d575ed.JPG&h=c28fefcc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"920634d428102383befb411df30e1d482ade2b9d","tid":1022790,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T05